{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "10.0",
      "line_index": 10,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f1dfeb6b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "──ぐううっ！！　うあ、ああああ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "13.0",
      "line_index": 13,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6ba357e5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "魔獣の苛烈な一撃に吹き飛ばされ、全身を地面に叩きつけられてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "13.2",
      "line_index": 13,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6ba357e5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "強烈な痛みが全身を襲うが、それでも立ち上がろうと全身に力を込める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "15.0",
      "line_index": 15,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7e64e385",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかし身体に力がまったく入らず、頭を強く打ったせいか意識が徐々に霞む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "17.0",
      "line_index": 17,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "4a8917f6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "獲物の打ちのめされた無残な姿に、咆哮を上げ勝利を確信する魔獣。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "17.2",
      "line_index": 17,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "4a8917f6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "トドメを刺そうとゆっくりと近づく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.0",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f77fad29",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（な、何とかしないと……このままじゃアイツに……や、やられる……！）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.0",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1fabb599",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "地面が揺れるほど力強く歩を進める魔獣。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "23.2",
      "line_index": 23,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "1fabb599",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もはや指先一つ動かせず、為す術が無くなってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.0",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "71d8dd08",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（もう……ダメだ……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "29.0",
      "line_index": 29,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bb2e6e0f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "死、その文字が脳裏をよぎり、諦めと恐怖にさらに意識が霞んでいく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "31.0",
      "line_index": 31,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ec11bbad",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "自分の意思とは無関係にゆっくりと瞼が閉じ始め、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "31.2",
      "line_index": 31,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "ec11bbad",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして全身から僅かに残っていた力が抜け落ちる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "33.0",
      "line_index": 33,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7dcda569",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その直後──。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.0",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "113a3c84",
      "speaker": "謎の少女",
      "ja": "──はぁっ！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "41.0",
      "line_index": 41,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1ae8d469",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "突如眩しい光が目の前を覆い、視界が真っ白になる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "43.0",
      "line_index": 43,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "34e36af",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "真っ白な視界の中で耳に入ってくる魔獣の雄たけび。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "43.2",
      "line_index": 43,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "34e36af",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかしその声にはさっきまでとは違い、恐怖の色が混じっていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "45.0",
      "line_index": 45,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d60c7b79",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして助けを求めるように小さく力強く吠えると、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "45.2",
      "line_index": 45,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d60c7b79",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その声がまったく聞こえなくなった。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "48.0",
      "line_index": 48,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7d5589b6",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "（いったい……何が……起こって……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "64.0",
      "line_index": 64,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ade28bee",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "う……あ……う、ぅ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "68.0",
      "line_index": 68,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "dbe67b19",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "いけない、もう命の灯が消えかかってる……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.0",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bebf983c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "でも大丈夫、私が必ず救ってみせますから……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.0",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d47f8796",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "少女は力強く{G_PlayerName}にそう告げると、衣服を丁寧に脱がしていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.2",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d47f8796",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "して少女自身も下着を脱ぐと、{G_PlayerName}の上に跨る。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "76.0",
      "line_index": 76,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "493632ee",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "お願い、死なないで……あと少しだけがんばって……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "94.0",
      "line_index": 94,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cbb20325",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふ、う……痛っ……うう……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "97.0",
      "line_index": 97,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f0a8e058",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "う……ぅう……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "100.0",
      "line_index": 100,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "25ec3b79",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "まだほとんど濡れていなかった秘部で、{G_PlayerName}の肉棒を受け入れる少女。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.0",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2bce81b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "痛みに僅かに顔を歪ませるが、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "102.2",
      "line_index": 102,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2bce81b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "『{G_PlayerName}を助ける』その強い意思で肉棒をすべて飲み込む。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "105.0",
      "line_index": 105,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1598339f",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だめ……まだ反応が弱い……。もっと刺激して……んっ！　国宝を活性化しないと……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.0",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cb2fdba2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "少女は何とか腰を動かそうとするもの、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "107.2",
      "line_index": 107,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "cb2fdba2",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "初めて男と一つになった不安と痛みからためらってしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "109.0",
      "line_index": 109,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "90454e3b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも目の前の、命の灯が小さくなっていく愛しい人のため、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "109.2",
      "line_index": 109,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "90454e3b",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "強い覚悟を決め、腰をゆっくりと動かし始める。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "117.0",
      "line_index": 117,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7de7e0d8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "う……んぅ♥　ふあ、あ……ああ……！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.0",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8901662c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ゆっくりとピストンを繰り返していく少女。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "119.2",
      "line_index": 119,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8901662c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "本人が思っている以上に痛みは無く、少し安堵する。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "121.0",
      "line_index": 121,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "335f612d",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかし──",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "124.0",
      "line_index": 124,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "30f19961",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "中……引っ掛かって……んあ……♥　これ……刺激が……んんっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.0",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e039d69",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "腰を動かすたびにカリが膣肉を削ぎ、初めての刺激に戸惑いを覚える。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.2",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e039d69",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "それでも少女は{G_PlayerName}の命を繋げるために、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "126.4",
      "line_index": 126,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "e039d69",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "さらに大きく腰を動かしていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "129.0",
      "line_index": 129,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "144337d8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "う……く……ふ、う……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "132.0",
      "line_index": 132,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8779c1d9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "少女の動きに呼応するかのように、{G_PlayerName}は小さく呻く。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "132.2",
      "line_index": 132,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "8779c1d9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "そして膣の刺激に肉棒もさらに大きくなり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "132.4",
      "line_index": 132,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "8779c1d9",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "甘い快感が無垢な少女の身体に襲い掛かる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.0",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d54667c1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ん……♥　反応……強まってきた……けどぉ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "135.2",
      "line_index": 135,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "d54667c1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "だめっ……♥　気持ち良く、なっちゃう……はぁ♥　はぁぁっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "137.0",
      "line_index": 137,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "887a28a3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "膣奥から自分でもはっきりわかるほど愛液が溢れ、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "137.2",
      "line_index": 137,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "887a28a3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "隙間から溢れてきたモノが{G_PlayerName}の下半身を濡らす。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.0",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "84bd8029",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ぐちゅぐちゅといやらしい水音がさらに強くなり、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "139.2",
      "line_index": 139,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "84bd8029",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "少女の膣奥が何かを求めるように強く疼いていた。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "142.0",
      "line_index": 142,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2b4cd1c3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "セックス、すごい……想像以上だよぉ……んんっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "142.2",
      "line_index": 142,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "2b4cd1c3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "やっぱりこの人は私の運命の人……だから絶対に助けなきゃ……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "144.0",
      "line_index": 144,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "75c130c3",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "少女はさらに強く腰を打ち付け、{G_PlayerName}の肉棒を膣で擦り上げる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "147.0",
      "line_index": 147,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5813f8e4",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふ……ふっ……ぐ、う、あ……！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.0",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "396997ac",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "命の灯が大きくなって……♥　もう少し……あと少し……♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "151.2",
      "line_index": 151,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "396997ac",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "はぁ♥　んはっ♥　あ、あっ！♥　ふあ、ああぁぁんっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.0",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5377619a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ダメぇ……この人のおちんちん気持ち良過ぎるぅ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "154.2",
      "line_index": 154,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "5377619a",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "あああ……♥　イっちゃう……イっちゃうよぉ……ふううっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "157.0",
      "line_index": 157,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "472fe6e1",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "はぁ……！　はぁ……！　うあ、あ……あああ……！！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "161.0",
      "line_index": 161,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6ba3315e",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "もう……ダメ……！♥　んぅ！♥　んあ、あっ♥　あああぁぁ～～っ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "172.0",
      "line_index": 172,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "10a9f196",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ふあぁっ！？♥　うあ、あ……あああっ……！！♥♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "174.0",
      "line_index": 174,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f94b51da",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "少女に導かれるように、白濁液がびゅるびゅると狭い膣奥に吐き出される。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "174.2",
      "line_index": 174,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "f94b51da",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "射精の勢い、量、そして熱さに少女も思わず達してしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.0",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6696f1fd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ううう……♥　す、ごい……！♥　これが男の人の……あうっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "177.2",
      "line_index": 177,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "6696f1fd",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "こんなに出るなんてぇ♥　この感覚っ！♥　耐えられないっ♥　んんっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "179.0",
      "line_index": 179,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "86ee0bf",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "いつまでも続くと思わせる射精、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "179.2",
      "line_index": 179,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "86ee0bf",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "しかしそれもすぐに収まり、同時に少女の表情が不安に染まっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "182.0",
      "line_index": 182,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "43ee6ca",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "んぅ♥　そんな……どうしてっ♥　まだ反応が弱いまま……ううっ♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "185.0",
      "line_index": 185,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "df900345",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "これ以上セックスすると……んっ！♥　私の方がおかしくなっちゃう♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.0",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "e510ac5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "{G_PlayerName}が射精を終えてもなお、小さな絶頂を繰り返し、身体を震わせ続ける少女。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.2",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 2,
      "line_hash": "e510ac5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "甘美な快感の連続に意識を失いそうになるものの、",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "187.4",
      "line_index": 187,
      "inline_index": 4,
      "line_hash": "e510ac5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "{G_PlayerName}の状態は好転せず、不安がどんどん少女の中で大きくなっていく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "190.0",
      "line_index": 190,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "61f3440c",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ダメ……ダメ……♥　死んではダメ……！♥　ダメなのぉっ！♥",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "198.0",
      "line_index": 198,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5fb5c1b8",
      "speaker": "",
